							},
							"condition": "the seller wants to see details"
						}
					],
					"documentation": "# Show Sale Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *user* insert a sell **key**.\n2. System displays the information associated to a **Sale** with this saleNumber **key** (**title**, **description**, **status**, **price**, **publicationDate and file**).\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n\n1. If there is any attribute with no value, the field will be empty."
				},
				{
					"_type": "UMLUseCase",
					"_id": "AAAAAAGdBSEB43fzRPs=",
					"_parent": {
						"$ref": "AAAAAAGMFaB678SNc/w="
					},
					"name": "Change Lenguage",
					"documentation": "# Change Lenguage Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *user* press the change the **lenguage button**.\n2. *user* select a lenguage options from the different option by pressing one the **buttons**.\n3. *System* changes the lenguage.\n\n\n## Alternative flow"
				},
