					"documentation": "# Login Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *non registrated* press the **login button**.\n2. *non registrated* write the **username** in the **username gap**.\n3. *non registrated* write the **password** in the **password gap**.\n4. *non registrated* press the **confirmation button**.\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n\n1. Some fields are **empty**. System informs the *non registrated*.\n2. The **username** doesn't exist in the **data-base**.  System informs the *non registrated*.",
