					"documentation": "# OfferDemand Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Registered* fills the **name** text box.\n2. *Registered* fills the **description** text box.\n3. *Registered* fills the **price** text box.\n4. *Registered* presses the **make demand** button.\n\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n\n1. one, two or all three text boxes are empty. System displays a message.",
